NOV 17-19 ill be showing and selling 30-35 originals included in @blackdaggerbooks vol 45 along with multiple full size finished red pencil studies. I’ll also have 5 new large prints with me, a bunch of drawings and be tattooing off some new sheets of flash. Grateful to have the opportunity to show all the paintings together as a whole. Come hang out and check them out, entry to the show is free and you can find any and all details @rosehillgiftshop page. There will be a full bar, food, coffee, drinks, and tattooing from a bunch of great tattooers from all over the country. Hope to see everyone there and please feel free to share the post! 🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼 (if you have any questions about purchasing the paintings feel free to message me) big thanks to my friend @nicksharratt for making it all happen

Couple days late, but, a sincere THANK YOU to everyone who took the time to come out, check out the gallery, purchased a painting or print, or just stopped by for a handshake or conversation. Huge thanks to @blackdaggerbooks for the opportunity to be a part of their project and coming out as well, couldn’t have asked for better folks to work with. And last but certainly not least thanks to @nicksharratt for an awesome weekend and putting an incredible show.
